<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ifindv's Blog</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on ifindv's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 ifindv</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ifindv.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：子代理（Subagents）</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-25-claude-code-tutorial-04-subagents/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-25-claude-code-tutorial-04-subagents/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;子代理是Claude Code可以委托任务给的专业化AI助手。每个子代理都有特定目的，使用与主对话分离的独立上下文窗口，并可以配置特定工具和自定义系统提示词。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：技能（Skills）</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-24-claude-code-tutorial-03-skills/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-24-claude-code-tutorial-03-skills/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;代理技能（Agent Skills）是可复用的、基于文件系统的功能，扩展了Claude的能力。它们将领域专业知识、工作流程和最佳实践打包成可发现的组件，当相关时Claude会自动使用这些组件。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：内存系统（Memory）</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-23-claude-code-tutorial-02-memory/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-23-claude-code-tutorial-02-memory/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;内存系统使Claude能够在多个会话和对话中保持持久化的上下文。与临时上下文窗口不同，内存文件允许你在团队间共享项目标准、存储个人开发偏好、维护特定目录的规则，并将外部文档导入为版本控制的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：斜杠命令</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-22-claude-code-tutorial-01-slash-commands/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-22-claude-code-tutorial-01-slash-commands/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;斜杠命令是Claude Code中最基础的快捷方式，通过 &lt;code&gt;/命令名&lt;/code&gt;的语法快速调用预定义功能。无论是内置命令还是自定义命令，都能让你在开发过程中更高效地与Claude交互。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2人目のダミー作者</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.ja/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.ja/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;2人目のダミー作者の素晴らしいダミープロフィールです。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dummy Second Author</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.de/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.de/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Die fantastische Beispielbiografie des zweiten Beispielautors.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dummy Second Author</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.es/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.es/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;La increíble biografía ficticia del segundo autor ficticio.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dummy Second Author</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.fr/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.fr/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;La super bio fictive du deuxième auteur fictif.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dummy Second Author</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.pt-br/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.pt-br/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A incrível bio fictícia do segundo autor fictício.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dummy Second Author</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/authors/secondauthor/_index.pt-pt/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000<